data.title: How long would it take to travel by sleigh from Odessa, Ukraine to Yekaterinburg (1454 miles) in 1930 winter?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 2): It is not the first time, and probably not the last when I’m giving a concise and nerdy answer to an utterly bogus question, but that’s the major part of the Quora fun.
